profile:
Clera Windows + Doors by FM Industries has been manufacturing and installing windows and doors throughout all of Ontario since 1978.  They add beauty and value to nearly 1000 homes every month and can easily service the entire province via one of their 37 sales and installation offices.

 

Clera Windows + Doors has been recognized as one of Canada’s Best 50 Privately Managed Companies and the City of Vaughan’s Company of the Year.  Clera was recently awarded the Houzz service award for 2014 and is a proud recipient of the Homestars Best Award for 2012 and 2013. Add to these achievements a stellar A+ Better Business Bureau rating and you’ll understand why Clera Windows + Doors is the best choice for new windows and doors for your home.

 

We manufacture.  We install.  You save.

Toronto, East York, Stratford, Goderich, Oshawa, Essex County, Pembroke, Ottawa East, Ottawa West, Kitchener, Orangeville, Welland, Barrie, Newmarket, Peterborough, Belleville, Cobourg, Kingston, Brantford, Guelph, Oakville, Mississauga, Kanata, Brockville, Woodstock, London, Cornwall, Burlington, Hamilton

profile:
WISE Home Improvements 
Exterior Renovations 
www.wisehomepro.com 
613 921-1256 

We supply and install the following: 

All TYPES OF SIDING renovations for your home. Available vinyl , custom wood, aluminum and steel. Supplied and installed all top brand name siding products such as Gentek, Kaycan, Mitten, LP Smart Side as well as many other brand names well known in the industry. All sidings come in a wide variety of colours and styles. 

STONE VENEER, STONE FACING Fusion stone is one of the most popular stone products with todays consumer. Available with mortar or dry stack both with different finished looks. Each product is unic and has its own manufacturers installation method which must be followed and understood for a proper install. 

EAVESTROUGH DOWNPIPES SOFFIT FASCIA CAPPING 
We install top brand name aluminum products to improve the appearance of the exterior perimeter of your home. Available in many colour options. Gentec, Kaycan, Mitten. We also have solid copper, Eaves, soffit and fascia available. 

VINYL WINDOWS 
Government approved, high quality, very competitive North Star vinyl thermal replacement windows. Available in all styles and glass options. Retro fit or brick to brick. ( Our brick to brick and or Tear out windows our very competitively priced ) 
Bay Windows - Bow Windows - Tilt Windows - Side slider Windows - Casement Windows - Double hung Windows - Vertical and Horizontal Windows - One Lite Windows 

REPLACEMENT DOORS 
STEEL INSULATED DOORS and FIBREGLASS INSULATED DOORS 
Steel insulated - fibreglass - R-series - new construction - garden - side lites, transoms and vinyl patio doors. Hundreds of styles, glass designs with all available options. 

Vinyl Patio Doors and Garden Doors 

KNOCK OUTS - Cut out a wall, existing window or door area to allow for a larger window or door to be installed. Make an exit from your back bedroom on to a deck into your back yard. 

All windows and doors are measured and installed according to each manufacturers requirements.  Its extremely important that this is followed as not to void manufacturing warranties or improper install. 

Do you already have your products ? 

 If you have already purchased windows, door, siding or stone products and need them installed call or E-mail for an install only quote. Don't forget to include your phone number in your e-mail. wisehomeimprovements@gmail.com or www.wisehomepro.com 


You can also visit us at www.wisehomepro.com
or e-mail at wisehomeimprovements@gmail.com 
613 921-1256 

36 years in the renovation industry. Very competitive. 
E-mail or call today for your free estimate. 
" Don't forget to include your address and phone number in your email " 
Ask for Jay ( 613 921-1256 ) 



Bonded 
Insured 
WSIB 
Install Certified 

Serving Hastings County - Prince Edward County And surrounding area 
Belleville - Trenton - Picton - Wellington - Quinte West - Foxboro - Madoc - Maramora Stirling - Frankford - Campbellford - Brighton - Warkworth - Hastings - Colborne - Napanee - Deseronto - Odessa - Tweed
